    one place footer content lives. Not view-transition-pinned (unlike the nav): it scrolls
    and slides with the page content, which is fine for a one-line footer. %>
<footer class="mt-16 pb-8 text-center text-xs text-neutral-600">
  <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors"><%= t('footer.privacy') %></a>
</footer>
<script src="/js/page-transitions.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>